title: v4.0 beta : Custom App modes and Firebase Support
message:
v4.0 beta : Custom App modes and Firebase Support

Huge change in coding philosophy. App is now more modular and flexible. Major change is with different modes. Now users will be able to see personalized UI and they get to choose which one they want. "Offline" and "Online" mode will play important role in future. Another important change is shifting database to Firebase. Now we have 'real' dynamic database. Though Firebase don't have support to proxy, we are trying to make work around. Still introducing new features from firebase will improve our app :)
